source.name: 2005-2007 American Community Survey Three-Year PUMS Housing File
source.description: National survey that collects data from a sample of the resident population in the United States. Housing units in every county in the United States and municipio in Puerto Rico. The sample also includes institutional and non-institutional group quarters.
